query:
INSERT INTO l2_to_l1_events
        (
            l1_token_addr,
            to_address,
            amount,
            l1_block_number,
            l2_block_number,
            tx_number_in_block
        )
        SELECT
            u.l1_token_addr,
            u.to_address,
            u.amount,
            u.l1_block_number,
            u.l2_block_number,
            u.tx_number_in_block
        FROM UNNEST(
            $1::bytea[],
            $2::bytea[],
            $3::numeric[],
            $4::bigint[],
            $5::bigint[],
            $6::integer[]
        ) AS u(
            l1_token_addr,
            to_address,
            amount,
            l1_block_number,
            l2_block_number,
            tx_number_in_block
        )
        ON CONFLICT (l1_block_number, l2_block_number, tx_number_in_block) DO NOTHING
